entry.name: catapult
entry.description: Catapult is a data transfer application, providing an alternative to FTP. Employing the power of both TCP and UDP, Catapult offers an optimal path for any network, regardless of latency or packet loss.

entry.name: dingtalk
entry.description: DingTalk is an enterprise communication and collaboration platform developed by Alibaba Group. It is one of the largest professional communication and management apps in China. This app-id covers traffic from the Dinktalk client.

entry.name: lucidchart
entry.description: Lucidchart is an online collaborative diagramming platform for chart creation and collaboration within a team. This app-id identifies traffic from the lucidchart web-browser client.

entry.name: mindmeister
entry.description: MindMeister is an online mind mapping application that allows its users to visualize, share and present mind maps in the cloud. This app-id identifies traffic from the mindmeister web-browser client.

entry.name: mineralt
entry.description: Mineralt is a javascript miner that is embedded in websites and uses CPU resources while you visit such sites to mine the monero cryptocurrency. This App-ID identifies such mining activity giving you the ability to get visibility into such traffic and block it in an enterprise environment.

entry.name: roblox
entry.description: Roblox is a large-scale online game creating and playing platform that allows users to design their own games and play games created by other users. The platform hosts social network games constructed of Lego-like virtual blocks.

entry.name: taobao
entry.description: Taobao is a Chinese online shopping website, headquartered in Hangzhou, and owned by Alibaba.

entry.name: webmine
entry.description: Webmine is a javascript miner that is embedded in websites and uses CPU resources while you visit such sites to mine the monero cryptocurrency. This App-ID identifies such mining activity giving you the ability to get visibility into such traffic and block it in an enterprise environment.

entry.name: wheniwork
entry.description: Wheniwork is an employee scheduling and communication platform. This app-id identifies traffic from the wheniwork web-browser client.

entry.name: wisestamp
entry.description: WiseStamp is an online email signature generator based on users' business profiles. WiseStamp allows users to design signatures and can integrate their signatures in different web mail providers such as Gmail, Hotmail, .etc.

entry.name: workable
entry.description: Workable is a recruiting software to manage hiring pipelines. This app-id identifies traffic from the workable web-browser client.
